  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0ba4\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4  \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb5\u0bc8 - \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The archaeological team will go to the Presidential Palace today to record the damaged items - data",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special team of the Department of Archeology will go to this place today (27) to record the cultural and antiquities that have been completely destroyed and damaged in the Presidential Palace.",
        "Assistant Director of Archeology (Western Province) Shyamali Rajapaksa of the Department of Archeology said that they will start these procedures as per the request made by the police.",
        "It is said that the protesters have taken over the Presidential Palace, Alary Palace and the Presidential Secretariat on the 9th of July and have damaged the antiquities in them.",
        "However, the department says that there are no records with the Department of Archeology regarding the antiquities in the Presidential Palace.",
        "It is worth noting that a special committee will go there today for records."
      ],
